data.text: Promised Land by Jack Dann 2007 SIGNED Limited 1st Edition; near fine hardcover book in near fine dust jacket; the book is clean, tight, square, and -- but for the author's signature and limitation number on the limitation page (see photo) -- free of any markings showing little to no additional evidence of having been previously gently read; unclipped dust jacket shows very light shelf wear but remains in near fine condition.
